                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Pur désir d'échapper à l'affreux terre-à-terre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "A ce joug du réel qui courbe et qui meurtrit.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Séducteur souverain, c'est ta main qui les aide",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "A secouer leur chaîne, à jeter leur fardeau,",
