                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Par un courant fatal poussés vers le mirage,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Ayant perdu leur lest, jeté leurs avirons,",
